'''sadd'''

saddo hi rit vhonkleger ani noureager zata .Hea riti rivazant eka mezar tambdde rongache lugott dourotat ani tache voir khursachi imaz va dhovea rongachea lugttacho khuris korun tambddea lugttacher dourotat . Toxench eke thalyent sakor ,abolechi fulam ani saibinnichi imaz dourotat kiteak tor tancho fuddar (vhonklecho ,noucho ) boro zaupak ani goddsannenn ani fulamni bhorpak .Uprant ximvpi saddeak kator laita ani ghorchi vhoddil magnne korta .Konn eklo baibol vachta ani magir vhonklek noureak saibinni lagi yeun magnne korpak sagta . Tanchi xezari ani tanchi ghorchi monxam punn odhik korun zanntti vhokle nou-yak besamv ditat ani saddeacher aple dan poixanchea rupan dourotat ani te dan uprant ximvpi vhorta .Vhonkleche vattin saddeacher ji saibinn dourotat ti saibinn vhonkleli auy bapuy tika ditat kallar saddeacher bomp partt saibinn(saibinn jichea hatant ballok jezu asa)dourotali.Tacho hetu oso, vhonkleche borem zavo tancho ghorabo bhurgea ballam soitouyor sorunk punn ata khoinchi-i saibinn va satanchi imaz saddeacher dourotat ani uprant tich imaz vhonkol denneak nou-yager dhaddtta.

